<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.6">
<l>vaḷḷi koḻunaṉ mutalāya makka ḷōṭu mukkaṇṇāṉ</l>
<l>veḷki yōṭa viṟalvāṇaṉ viyaṉṟōḷ vaṉattait tuṇittukantāṉ</l>
<l>paḷḷi kamalat tiṭaippaṭṭa pakuvā yalavaṉ mukamnōkki</l>
<l>naḷḷi yūṭum vayalcūḻnta naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who was contented, having chopped down the forest</l>
<l rend="indent">of wide[-spread] arms of brave Bāṇa,</l>
<l>As the three-eyed one, [along] with the first of [his] children, Vaḷḷi’s husband,</l>
<l rend="indent">being shamed, ran away,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr surrounded by fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where a [female] crab pouts,</l>
<l>Glancing toward the face of the large-mouthed male</l>
<l rend="indent">who was stuck inside [his] lotus [bed] chamber.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
